<div id="review_3132960841" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3132960841" />
    <a title="Caleb Roehrig" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/41775673-caleb-roehrig"><img alt="Caleb Roehrig" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1493188414p2/41775673.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3132960841?book_show_action=true">Jan 19, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Caleb Roehrig" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Caleb Roehrig" href="/user/show/41775673-caleb-roehrig">Caleb Roehrig</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=male-protagonist">male-protagonist</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=ya">ya</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=lgbt">lgbt</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=female-protagonist">female-protagonist</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=multiple-pov">multiple-pov</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41775673-caleb-roehrig?shelf=set-in-canada">set-in-canada</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3132960841" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9555613206892339227">I can already tell this is a book I’ll be bringing up for a long time, because I feel like I’ve got too much to say to put my thoughts together coherently. It’s about all the ways in which queerness is a unique and personal experience, but also about how it unites and creates community out of diverse identities. It celebrates queer history, and it celebrates queer modernity, and it captures the beauty of what it means to be born under the rainbow. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


